"Of course Mighty Hydras." SKY SHADOW said with a bow. "As you command."
SKY SHADOW intoned and then spoke to the computer, "Computer. Location
of Tarantulus."

There was a short pause before it replied. "Tarantulus is located in
cargo bay four."  SKY SHADOW chuckled wickedly. "Ahhh, cargo bay four.
I thought he had something going on down there."

MEANWHILE IN CARGO BAY 4:

TARANTULUS stood in the darkness for a moment as a previously hidden
door slid open revealing a dimly lit chamber of some sort inside.

"Ahhh yes my sweet." TARANTULUS said as he stepped inside and looked
almost lovingly at a modified CR chamber in the middile of the room.
All sorts of cables and tubes were running to it and it looked to be
in a count down.

The rest of the room was a mish mash of computer and machinery parts
that lined the shelves. Spare diodes and servos where placed on
shelves along the wall on one side, while on the other was a large
computer work station that looked as if it had been cobbled together.
Part of it had cables that were running to the CR chamber in the room.

TARANTULUS cackled to himself as the timer on the CR chamber was
finishing its count down and then finally beeped indicating it was
'done'. With a deft movement he pressed a button on a nearby console
and the door of the chamber hissed and clicked and slowly began to
open.

"Awaken my sweet." TARANTULUS said as he waited for the result. "Return to me."
